{"type": "article", "id": 33184, "title": "竟然有人做了透明的机顶盒｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-10-11T23:32:18Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 33021, "name": "SSTEEL"}, {"id": 33818, "name": "Closca"}, {"id": 33819, "name": "Studio Pedrazzi"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 77, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161011171258EmMxHC6huo7bO1tW.jpg", "contents": "<p class=\"\">          </p><p>          </p><p class=\"\">「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Fuga by Closca</h3><p>          </p><p>冬天骑车的时候是不是觉得有点冷飕飕的？自行车头盔品牌 <a href=\"http://closca.co/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Closca</a> 最近为旗下的折叠式头盔 Fuga 推出了配套的毛线帽。Fuga 头盔本身是一个在 2013 年集资成功的众筹项目，采用泡沫混凝土制成，展开后光滑圆润的造型看上去颇具时尚气息。三层式的结构可以从上往下聚合在一起，让收纳变得更加轻松。这是头盔的<a href=\"http://closca.co/products/closca-fuga\" rel=\"nofollow\">购买链接</a>，售价为 140 到 170 美元不等，<a href=\"http://closca.co/products/accessories\" rel=\"nofollow\">毛线帽</a>的价格为 45 美元，有米色和灰色可选。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610111547468A5VWMhlURsHfqC9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714844\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011154746iadCDA7XwlhWb8v3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011154746RL1O8jrwBCodYzUx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011154746MPA9fYDOC7IuBbWe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011154746FxfTbp7HyO1wdJtl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011154746Yyn7hIl8dqxjAF2t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.714844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Bent by Studio Pedrazzi</h3><p>          </p><p>不锈钢和手工毛毯搭配在一起的家具会是什么样子？巴西设计工作室 <a href=\"http://studiopedrazzi.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Pedrazzi</a> 最近利用这两种材质本身的属性成功打造了一套结合了造型与功能的家具系列 Bent。这套家具由一张椅子和三张凳子组成，经过切割后的不锈钢在弯曲后被焊接在一起，外面再覆盖上通过传统织布机手工制作而成的毛毯。配合钢制结构，毛毯上的线条也遵从了简洁的风格，让人同时感受到金属的冰冷和毛料的温暖。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610111549193belQIhG0ifYEFBX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.732274\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011154919Yn76GxPhbEJR0V1U.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.592910\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011154920aiAkInBl0JPWUfNr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.909535\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011154919sQryoh5Xeu7q9ZUK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011154920wKD6zUXYBxSWpr3d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.591687\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011154920fnuUxCSXieLTA5Ml.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.909535\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>I/O by Dustin Lee</h3><p>          </p><p>很多人嫌电视机顶盒太难看，但又没办法把它藏起来。加拿大设计师 <a href=\"http://www.dustinlee.ca/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dustin Lee</a>&nbsp;因此有了一个&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/43481607/IO\" rel=\"nofollow\">I/O</a> 机顶盒概念设计。Lee 的想法是创造一个能让人们了解设备运作的窗口，普通的消费者可以透过透明的外壳一窥此前不太常见的机盒构造，感受到独特的科技美学。为了突出接口区域，Lee 在这个部分插入了一个上色的覆膜铝盒，顶部的点矩阵还能配合当前的操作显示出不同的图标。不过这基本上是个没什么用的设计，因为机顶盒透不透明根本不是我们的选择。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011155130Mr7ATGfiX3bZaIxW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011155130RZIvc32fbj6CpwED.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011155131k4oB0j1d2bJcCe7H.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011155132mth7nHWSf38gYbJ0.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664286\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011155131NZR8WPy6s4kDcUeQ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011155132pLo4g8KmAv7rExTb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.560000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Orbit 360 by I AM Cardboard</h3><p>          </p><p>现在要拍摄全景照片并不是什么非常困难的事情，一些智能手机已经具备了这个功能。然而要完美拍出一张全景照片，手抖就是第一个要克服的难题。香港的 VR 设备公司 <a href=\"http://www.imcardboard.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">I AM Cardboard</a> 最近就针对这个情况推出了一款名为 Orbit 360 的手机支架，收起时它是一个体积小巧的圆形底座，展开后放上配对的手机就能通过蓝牙遥控器进行远程操作。支架本身有着 180 度的调整范围，配合 360 度旋转的底座，让你可以轻松地拍摄到想要的全景照片。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/imcardboard/orbit-360-a-better-way-to-take-spherical-panoramas\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 70 美元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011160706nhY4qAGfditepDjN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.532641\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011160706LkD54N2ywt7MUbzj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.928678\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011160706QrxmfHS1u0bCoWqe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.000000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610111607067z5tJ9YFycgUZRBs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.930576\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Geometry Vase &amp; Candle by Mario Tsai</h3><p>          </p><p>如果你喜欢几何形的装饰品，不妨看看这套由杭州 <a href=\"http://www.zzdesignstudio.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Mario Tsai</a> 工作室带来的 <a href=\"http://www.zzdesignstudio.com/geometry-vasecandle-holder.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Geometry</a> 烛台和花器。这个系列由大理石和黄铜制成的三角体、圆柱体和球体构成，可以组合成多种不同的造型，有一些看上去仿佛处在动态和静止间临界状态，相当微妙。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201610111557591H0Nkb8rPiq2FTKG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011155759kFoMRH5fJQE7bKpd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011155800xI8aePDLBZXspH7F.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011155800gMbfoCyXSqEvWR92.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.706667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>POP-UP by SSTEEL</h3><p>          </p><p>金属家具品牌 <a href=\"http://www.ssteeldesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">SSTEEL</a> 最近将立体书的概念运用到灯具设计上，推出了这款名为 POP-UP 的台灯。它并没有传统意义上的灯罩和底座，像是折纸一样的金属板将光源包围在内。亮灯后会让人产生它是立体的错觉，设计简单却不失趣味。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011160610lnSiX2MDv5LCp0Yd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.713889\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016101116061064Bg3jVowNrDkLvs.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"png\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011160610kvoxhe70HKdfqAi8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.944444\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011160610dyzGD6LTfU0vK7Mm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161011160610M3q9gPLabGQHoksv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.662500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}